_van_den_Hoogenband\"}, {\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.839438936655394e-53, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999998058306308, \"rank\": 1.9416945598133156e-07, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two decades\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"the last race\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"that billing\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"that order\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"fractions\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky is playing down her chances over the shorter distance - three years after Titmus won in Tokyo in a thriller, her first individual loss at the Games.\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 1887, \"end\": 1892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9964929705712096, \"rank\": 0.0035193408079647634, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngr